<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="56">Geographical distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="56">It would appear from the few records available that this species is present in the Western Cape, South Africa. The accuracy of the determination of the single specimen from Zimbabwe has not been determined.</paragraph>
